name: 18-inch_Shaker_Series_On_the_Wall_Cabinet_
description:
Spice up your kitchen with this on-the-wall cabinet. This cabinet sits on concealed hinges leaving the door undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open in either direction. Perfect for use of spices, medicine or just storage.
